Network-Use Disclosure (AGPL-3.0 §13)
-------------------------------------

If a build of this backend is offered to users over a network, those
users must be given access to the corresponding source code of the
running version. The recommended way to fulfill this is:

  - Display a prominent, persistent link to this repository (pinned to
    the running commit SHA) in the application's user interface or
    a dedicated /about endpoint.
  - Document the running commit SHA in container image labels:
    `org.opencontainers.image.source` and
    `org.opencontainers.image.revision`.
